# Project Structure

## Directory Organization

- **src/**: Main source code directory
  - **pages/**: Page components for different routes
  - **components/**: Reusable UI components
    - **ui/**: ShadCN UI components
    - **sections/**: Larger composed sections of the UI
  - **assets/**: Static assets like images, fonts, etc.
  - **lib/**: Utility functions, configurations, and helpers
  - **hooks/**: Custom React hooks
  - **blocks/**: Building blocks of the application

## Configuration Files

- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Dependencies and scripts
- [vite.config.ts](mdc:vite.config.ts) - Vite configuration
- [tailwind.config.ts](mdc:tailwind.config.ts) - TailwindCSS configuration
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration
